---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Knowledge
description: "Briefs, field notes, and shared thinking emerging from The Future Herd."
heroImage: "/assets/img/knowledge-hero.png"
heroAlt: "A visual representation of shared knowledge and interconnected systems"
heroCaption: "A growing commons of ideas, insights, and leadership thinking"
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-image">
    <img
      src="{{ heroImage }}"
      alt="{{ heroAlt }}"
      loading="eager"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="hero-content">
    <h1>{{ title }}</h1>
    <p class="tagline">{{ description }}</p>
  </div>
</section>

<p>
This is a growing commons of leadership briefs and shared thinking emerging from conversations on <em>The Future Herd</em>.
These artifacts are designed to stand on their own, while remaining connected to the dialogues that shaped them.
</p>

<ul class="knowledge-list">
{% for item in collections.knowledge | reverse %}
  <li>
    <h2><a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.data.title }}</a></h2>
    {% if item.data.subtitle %}<p><strong>{{ item.data.subtitle }}</strong></p>{% endif %}
    <p>{{ item.data.abstract }}</p>
  </li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>
